{"cid":"1598506744535063","cha_name":"有你在身边就很美","desc":"“想和你一起看一场演唱会，想你难过时在我怀中流泪，想和你背包走遍天南地北……”你的身边有没有这样的一个人，你们一起走过埋头苦读的青葱岁月，一起背着背包走遍天南地北，TA难过时你在身边，你闪耀时也有TA作陪，你们在一起，就是最完美的阵容。一直陪在你身边的那个人，又是谁呢？不管是朋友、恋人还是家人，快和你的那个TA一起录出你们的“陪伴”吧！\n——身边有你的陪伴，人生才算圆满啊。","schema":"aweme://aweme/challenge/detail?cid=1598506744535063","author":{"uid":"6796248446","short_id":"52","nickname":"抖音小助手","gender":1,"signature":"本宝宝暂时还没想到个性签名","avatar_larger":{"uri":"1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p3.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p26.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p9.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_thumb":{"uri":"100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p29.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p26.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p6.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_medium":{"uri":"720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p3.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p29.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p9.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"birthday":"","is_verified":true,"follow_status":0,"aweme_count":0,"following_count":0,"follower_count":0,"favoriting_count":0,"total_favorited":0,"is_block":false,"hide_search":true,"constellation":10,"location":"","hide_location":false,"weibo_verify":"","custom_verify":"","unique_id":"douyin","bind_phone":"","special_lock":0,"need_recommend":0,"is_binded_weibo":false,"weibo_name":"","weibo_schema":"","weibo_url":"","story_open":false,"story_count":0,"has_facebook_token":false,"has_twitter_token":false,"fb_expire_time":0,"tw_expire_time":0,
